markdownRemark.html: Situated in Casares, between Marbella and Sotogrande, just 45 minutes from Malaga airport and a few kilometers from Gibraltar. This course climbs up steeply on the first part. A buggy is a must for most people. The greens are wide and it is an attractive area.
